# Bismuth Token + Component Source Map

This PEN is the implementation bridge between design artifacts and code.

## Token map

- `color.surface` -> `src/lib/constants/colors.ts` (surface/background scale)
- `color.accent` -> `src/lib/constants/colors.ts` (primary accent actions)
- `space.2`, `space.3` -> `src/lib/constants/layout.ts` (spacing rhythm)
- `radius.md` -> `src/lib/constants/layout.ts` (shared medium radius)

## Component map

- `Shell/Sidebar` -> `src/lib/ui/sidebar-shell.svelte`
- `Navigation/Item` -> `src/lib/ui/sidebar-shell.svelte` (navigation row patterns)
- `Editor/Toolbar` -> `src/lib/hubs/editor/components/EditorToolbar.svelte`
- `Editor/Surface` -> `src/lib/hubs/editor/components/NoteEditor.svelte`

## Property conventions

- Component property names use lowerCamelCase.
- Use typed domains:
  - `boolean` for toggles
  - `string` for freeform text
  - `enum` with explicit `options` for controlled values
  - `instance-swap` for cross-component reference ids

## Constraint conventions

- Prefer explicit presets via MCP:
  - `fixed` for stable controls
  - `pin-left-right` for top bars
  - `fill` for primary content panes
  - `stretch` for repeating list rows
- Snapshot parity depends on `resizeResolution` metadata in resolved instance payloads.
